+ * AV1 cells are emitted at min mode-info (4x4) granularity. A coding block
+ * spans a variable number of these cells per its bsize; the consumer collapses
+ * equal-block cells the way HEVC collapses by cu_log2. Dispatched on
+ * codec_id == AV1. QP carries libaom's per-block current_qindex (0..255);
+ * motion vectors are in 1/8-pel luma units (col=x, row=y).
+ */
